lines.text: You know, I came in the shower this morning without touching myself?

[speaks into telephone]
Martin Bormann's Super Service.
Who the hell is this?
SuperLorna.
Get off the line, bitch!
I'm gonna strap on your old man!

[answers phone]
Martin Bormann's Super Service!
Jawohl!
Can I... take it out in trade?
Credit cards or cash!
What do you use?
What do you got?
I'd recommend 10-40.
Sounds like a good number.
Like I were saying, how does my beautiful body look today?
Dynamite baby, dynamite!
Is the fucking we get worth the fucking we get?
[after Harry's "faulty" dynamite re-ignites and blows him up]
Leapin' lizards!
[referring to Clint who is fleeing the sticks of dynamite Harry is hurling at him]
He ain't gonna finish last 'cause he ain't gonna finish at all. You can't make a throughbred out of a jackass.
I work out everyday. A man's got to keep in shape.

[seductively bouncing on a mattress]
I know a better way.
[to Supervixen who is chained spreadeagled on a mountain top]
What you need is a long fuse and a big bang. Warm milk fetches the old barn cat, sweet grapes will get you a possum, and this will bring him back.
[lights the fuse to a stick of dynamite and sets the charge between Supervixen's thighs]
It's been fun. This'll be the biggest and last bang you'll ever have.
